                "traits": {
                    "rarity": "common",
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "Vcb2fzxMkjOhWNPz",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Drain Potential",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The morrowkin tries to drain the motivation from its target, who must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:31] save. If the target fails, it is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 2} on a critical failure) and must roll twice and use the worse result on all checks for 1 minute. Creatures wearing a hope talisman are unaffected.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "rarity": "common",
                    "value": [
                        "misfortune",
                        "void"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "sxD01nPswudJsjzS",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Swallow Future",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The morrowkin inhales and draws forth the future deeds of all creatures around it. All creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] of the morrowkin take [[/r (6d8 + 18)[mental]]] damage and must attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:39] save.</p>\n<p>The morrowkin can't Swallow Future again for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>Creatures wearing hope talismans can choose to let their hope talisman break in order to ignore the effect after seeing the result of their Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 4} (likely causing it to die immediately).</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "rarity": "common",
                    "value": [
                        "mental",
                        "void"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "pAa1q5ts9oP6qdky",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Tomorrow's Fury",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
